divs: Sighting DetailsI in the car beside my girl when i saw an object in the sky going downwards followed by maybe smoke. As we rode on i could see a couple more going in different directions. The closeup pic i zoomed in and the other i didn't touch. After about twenty minutes i could no longer see because of trees. I didn't feel shocked because this was my third time seeing a Ufo
Summary: Disk shaped objects going downward followed by trail of smoke and the other going in weird patterns
trends: There have been no other sightings in Argyle
This sighting has never been favorited.
